TY  - JOUR
TI  - Stability in Voting
AU  - Dummett, Michael
AU  - Farquharson, Robin
AB  - [Voting is presented as an n-person majority game, in which preferences are ordinal. A condition on the preferences, substantially weaker than one postulated by D. Black, is shown to be sufficient for "stability" in such games.]
